Key = "affinity"
Title = "Elemental Affinity"
Description = "All characters have [?element]elements[/?] they are resistant against, taking less [?damage]damage[/?] and more [?heal]healing[/?] from skills of the corresponding [?element]element[/?]. Symmetrically, they also have [?element]elements[/?] against which they are weak.
Humans usually have two resistances and two weaknesses, and they are not correlated with the character's [?skill]skills[/?].
[center]
